UPDATES:
---------
06/Dec : Mavenized and disted verion 0.0.1 

ABOUT
------
Contains coder/decoders for protobuf ( http://code.google.com/p/protobuf/ ) to other formats like json.

Contains :
 - A framework to plug in additional codecs for protobuf
 - A JSON codec implementation, which uses jackson as the underlying json processor.
 
 
USAGE
-------
	Codec codec=new JsonCodec()
	codec.setFeature(Feature.CLOSE_STREAM, true)
	codec.fromMessage(Message, OutputStream)
	Message =codec.toMessage(Class<Message>,InputStream)
		
- Check out the test cases for more details


GETTING TO WORK WITH MAVEN
-------------------------------
- Add the below repository in your pom file
  	<repositories>
  	....
		<repository>
			<id>protobuf-codec</id>
			<url>http://github.com/sijuv/protobuf-codec/raw/master/dist</url>
		</repository>
    ....
	</repositories>

- Add dependency to protobuf-codec
	<dependencies>
	....
		<dependency>
			<groupId>com.google.protobuf</groupId>
			<artifactId>codec</artifactId>
			<version><the version #></version>
		</dependency>
	....
	</dependencies>
		

 
BUILDING
----------
Prerequisites :
 - Needs Maven
 - Needs protoc to run test cases. http://code.google.com/apis/protocolbuffers/docs/proto.html#generating


DEPENDENCIES :
- Jackson for json parsing. [ see pom for details ]
 
BUGS & ISSUES
---------------
Raise bugs/issues on git


LIMITATIONS
--------------
- UnknownFieldSet not supported.



